net.sf.appia.management
Interface ManagedSession

All Known Implementing Classes:
PrimaryViewSession, RemoteAddressSession, SslCompleteSession, SuspectSession, SwitchingSession, TcpCompleteSession, ThroughputSession, TotalTokenSession
public interface ManagedSession

This class defines a ManagedSession. A managed session is a session that can receive new property values from the respective managed channel.

Version:
1.0
